  <body>

    <div id="container">

      <div id="inner">

        <h1 id="header">You're already in!</h1>

        <p>
          You have requested an invite to Webistor, and we noticed that
          {{#if invitation.author.username}}you have already been invited by {{invitation.author.username}}!
          {{else}}our team has already accepted your prior request.{{/if}}
        </p>

        <p>
          All you have to do is finish your account by clicking the button below:
        </p>

        <p id="button">
          <a href="http://www.webistor.net/register/{{invitation.token}}" target="_blank">
            Create your account
          </a>
        </p>

        <p>
          As with every one of our emails, just hit reply and we'll respond right away! :)
        </p>

        <p class="bold"> - The Webistor team</p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </body>
